{"tid":2456121,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"My Little Airport - 那陣時不知道 置身的日子都發亮","createTime":"2021-03-21T16:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T04:23:17.000Z","uid":174829,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c0fdba6a7d1d665eaad0d10709e62694e2fcfc","tid":2456121,"uid":174829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:08:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5xi49OreS3k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5xi49OreS3k&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=70ebb65a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5xi49OreS3k</a><br />\n<br />\n曲詞編  林阿p<br />\n唱  nicole au<br />\n和  karena au<br />\n<br />\n如像九十年代初<br />\n照片裡海灘的印象<br />\n那種下午沒有重量<br />\n帶點迷惘奔向夕陽<br />\n<br />\n那年獨自去南洋<br />\n一杯白咖啡的早上<br />\n四周是可冒險方向<br />\n尤加利樹葉的香<br />\n<br />\n那陣時不知道<br />\n置身的日子都發亮<br />\n眼光裡藏著的囂張<br />\n往後已不再同樣<br />\n<br />\n圖書館木製的窗<br />\n訓導假裝嚴肅的模樣<br />\n還未有傾訴對象<br />\n仍未覺得悲涼<br />\n<br />\n那陣時不知道<br />\n每天在風光的戰場<br />\n騎著馬去到邊疆<br />\n所到之地全是賜賞<br />\n<br />\nwoo 寂靜 但不漫長<br />\nwoo 寂靜 但不漫長<br />\nwoo 寂靜 但不漫長<br />\nwoo 寂靜 但不漫長<br />\nwoo"},{"pid":"f7f307585126545bcbb76ea60adf1d2e5eaed92c","tid":2456121,"uid":10056,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起以前細個放假ON居居無野做周圍行..果陣已經係最無憂無慮既生活"},{"pid":"bc429d5032de90e1ef9fbd034f50513f8ed188ee","tid":2456121,"uid":287830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d8c60eaab0583a6317f115c23586cc4a821c76","tid":2456121,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7f307585126545bcbb76ea60adf1d2e5eaed92c","tid":2456121,"uid":10056,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起以前細個放假ON居居無野做周圍行..果陣已經係最無憂無慮既生活"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"我80後尾班<br />\n嗰時好想大個<br />\n有自己嘅生活同事業<br />\n<br />\n而家諗返轉頭，真係覺得好傻<br />\n冇好好珍惜嗰段無所事事嘅日子<br />\n冇好好發掘周圍，而家好多都已經清拆嘅事物<br />\n只係一味想快啲長大<br />\n<br />\n所有嘢都物事人非"}]}